
<div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="jumbotron home-jumbo">
      <button type="button" id="sidebarCollapse" class="btn btn-yours-minimal">
        <i class="fas fa-align-left"></i>
        <!-- <span >MENU</span> -->
      </button>
      <div class="jumbo-cta">
        <h2> Solve The Future </h2>
        <p class="lead"> Weekly problem-solving podcasts featuring a diverse mix of thought leaders</p>
        <button type="button" class="btn-yours-minimal">
          <span>LISTEN</span>
        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="scroller">
        <div class="chevron"></div>
        <div class="chevron"></div>
        <div class="chevron"></div>
        <!-- <span class="text">Scroll down</span> -->
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row row-no-padding home-top-content">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-lg-4 ml-auto">
      <div class="col-xs-12 home-text-content" id="dynamic-margin">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-start">
          <h1 class="h1-a">Solve The Future</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-end">
          <p style="max-width: 75%">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Fuga incidunt expedita, quo molestias sapiente inventore hic totam consectetur saepe deleniti commodi consequuntur quae, natus error non asperiores quas ut officia.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 home-text-content">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-start">
          <h1 class="h1-b">Solutions-driven podcasts</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-end">
          <p style="max-width: 75%">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Nulla tenetur esse, sunt, ipsa porro consequatur sequi quibusdam! Quasi similique possimus unde, ad perspiciatis repellat dolores eveniet dolorum doloremque. Dolorem, ratione.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-6">
      <%= image_tag("stairway-to-ftr") %>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<script type="text/javascript">
  // only use this format for desktop
  if (screen.width > 480) {
  // calc height of text divs
  var textItems = document.getElementsByClassName('home-text-content');
  var textHeight = 0
  for (var i = textItems.length - 1; i >= 0; i--) {
    textHeight += textItems[i].clientHeight;
  };
  // set margin-top of text divs row to be (100vh - textHeight)
  document.getElementById('dynamic-margin').style.marginTop = `calc(100vh - ${textHeight}px)`;
  }

</script>
